-Knock, knock.
-Rohit?

1147
01:29:18.687 --> 01:29:22.980 line:82%
What did you do to bring Papa around?

1148
01:29:24.818 --> 01:29:26.326 line:82%
I fell in love with you.

1149
01:29:28.572 --> 01:29:31.185 line:82%
