Honestly, I was surprised.

1153
01:30:03.487 --> 01:30:04.650 line:82%
How to explain this?

1154
01:30:06.293 --> 01:30:08.362 line:82%
Deep inside the scoundrel Sanjay Malhotra,

1155
01:30:08.445 --> 01:30:11.338 line:82%
