to bring him out.

1157
01:30:19.832 --> 01:30:24.895 line:82%
Like you, he's also a fool,
being honest, being truthful.

1158
01:30:25.587 --> 01:30:27.700 line:82%
But it's only a matter of a few minutes...

1159
01:30:30.534 --> 01:30:32.219 line:82%
