01:45:02.178 --> 01:45:04.153 line:82%
-Do you realize what you've done?
-What?

1323
01:45:04.245 --> 01:45:08.334 line:82%
My bachelor party cost Rohit far less
than what your stupidity has cost me.

1324
01:45:09.929 --> 01:45:12.932 line:82%
-Darling, indeed.
-Are you done?

1325
01:45:14.080 --> 01:45:15.705 line:82%
Now, shut up and listen.

1326
01:45:15.798 --> 01:45:17.270 line:82%
You're in love with Anjali, right?

1327
01:45:17.353 --> 01:45:19.849 line:82%
