1356
01:46:58.079 --> 01:46:59.542 line:82%
Did you tell me about Rohit?

1357
01:47:00.056 --> 01:47:01.566 line:82%
I told you about my wedding.

1358
01:47:01.941 --> 01:47:04.407 line:82%
