1370
01:47:42.889 --> 01:47:45.412 line:82%
No, she's fine. She's a sweet girl.

1371
01:47:46.435 --> 01:47:48.629 line:82%
Sweet, my foot. I don't like her.

1372
01:47:48.754 --> 01:47:52.231 line:82%
