1424
01:51:13.836 --> 01:51:14.960 line:82%
Modern.

1425
01:51:17.046 --> 01:51:22.640 line:82%
He lives in Bombay,
how could Sanjay like anyone else?

1426
01:51:23.452 --> 01:51:27.223 line:82%
You're cosmopolitan too. From America.

1427
01:51:27.306 --> 01:51:28.408 line:82%
I'm different.

1428
01:51:29.141 --> 01:51:32.682 line:82%
I always wanted someone simple.
Like Anjali.

1429
01:51:34.129 --> 01:51:37.699 line:82%
But Sanjay and Ria make sense.

1430
01:51:42.588 --> 01:51:46.117 line:82%
-They look great together, don't they?
-Yes, great.

1431
01:51:46.200 --> 01:51:51.624 line:82%
They should get married
the same day as us.

1432
